so you can grow nice and tall?

00:21:12.376 --> 00:21:13.210
No, thanks.

00:21:13.877 --> 00:21:14.711
Okay.

00:21:25.305 --> 00:21:26.139
Where did they go?

00:21:27.891 --> 00:21:29.142
Darn it.

00:21:42.030 --> 00:21:43.532
This is so exhausting.

00:21:44.282 --> 00:21:46.118
Do you like that? Does that feel good?

00:21:46.201 --> 00:21:47.327
Oh, look at you.

00:21:47.411 --> 00:21:49.454
You love it, don't you?

00:21:51.581 --> 00:21:52.416
Ji-hye.

00:22:07.639 --> 00:22:08.723
You still haven't quit?

00:22:17.399 --> 00:22:18.650
I thought you did.

00:22:24.281 --> 00:22:25.198
I did.

00:22:26.658 --> 00:22:28.535
But someone made me start again.

00:22:29.244 --> 00:22:30.245
I'm to blame?

00:22:31.580 --> 00:22:34.291
How did I end up
at your wedding reception?

00:22:35.167 --> 00:22:36.710
Last Christmas…

00:22:39.171 --> 00:22:41.715
we were staying in a suite
at this very hotel.

00:22:43.383 --> 00:22:45.719
Your father is to blame for that.

00:22:45.802 --> 00:22:48.221
He probably ordered you to attend today.

00:22:48.305 --> 00:22:52.184
And you're a sweet daughter
who listens to her father's every word.

00:22:56.730 --> 00:22:57.814
It's a compliment.

00:22:58.690 --> 00:23:00.775
I've always liked that about you.

00:23:00.859 --> 00:23:02.944
You work so hard to be
an obedient daughter.

00:23:03.653 --> 00:23:04.988
And you know your place.

00:23:06.198 --> 00:23:08.617
Being his dead lover's secret child…

00:23:11.119 --> 00:23:12.287
doesn't seem to hinder you one bit.

00:23:17.250 --> 00:23:18.710
So that was it?

00:23:22.714 --> 00:23:24.382
That's why you kept our relationship
a secret the whole time.

00:23:26.718 --> 00:23:27.552
Why?

00:23:30.138 --> 00:23:31.890
Were you worried
I might hinder your future?

00:23:36.228 --> 00:23:37.312
I'm sorry.

00:23:37.896 --> 00:23:40.315
I'm too ambitious to risk
being weighed down by you.

00:23:40.982 --> 00:23:42.192
But don't worry.

00:23:42.776 --> 00:23:44.361
Your secret is safe with me.

00:23:45.153 --> 00:23:47.781
We might not become family,

00:23:48.323 --> 00:23:50.784
but I hope we can still be friends
who cheer each other on.

00:24:03.964 --> 00:24:05.340
I thought you were in the US.

00:24:05.882 --> 00:24:07.592
I'm here for a short business trip.

00:24:08.343 --> 00:24:09.344
And to see you.

00:24:12.973 --> 00:24:15.809
I'm sure you heard about my divorce.

00:24:19.062 --> 00:24:20.063
I missed you.

00:24:22.607 --> 00:24:23.858
What do you want?

00:24:23.942 --> 00:24:25.402
I came to treat you to a meal.

00:24:26.820 --> 00:24:28.154
I hear you're a director now.

00:24:29.072 --> 00:24:30.282
I'm so proud of you.

00:24:30.907 --> 00:24:32.117
There's no need to be.

00:24:32.993 --> 00:24:34.369
It's all thanks to you.

00:24:35.120 --> 00:24:37.580
I learned the hard way
that the only way to stop people

00:24:38.623 --> 00:24:40.583
from looking down on me
as the illegitimate child

00:24:40.667 --> 00:24:42.585
was to prove my worth
through my abilities.

00:24:44.254 --> 00:24:45.755
Do you know why I left you?

00:24:48.008 --> 00:24:49.134
You had

00:24:49.884 --> 00:24:51.594
an uncanny resemblance to them.

00:24:53.013 --> 00:24:53.847
Your eyes, to be precise.

00:24:57.475 --> 00:24:59.227
On the surface,
you acted like you weren't,

00:24:59.853 --> 00:25:01.479
but you were always anxious

00:25:02.731 --> 00:25:04.065
and craved affection.

00:25:07.027 --> 00:25:10.030
But I see you've changed a lot
since I last saw you.

00:25:10.989 --> 00:25:11.906
I can now see

00:25:13.366 --> 00:25:14.409
greed in your eyes.

00:25:17.245 --> 00:25:18.330
Now that you know, you can leave.

00:25:19.497 --> 00:25:21.416
I have no interest in mind games anymore.

00:25:33.428 --> 00:25:35.347
GO YEONG-SIK
APRIL 27, 2025

00:25:40.518 --> 00:25:41.436
There we go.

00:25:47.317 --> 00:25:48.735
"Go Yeong-sik"?

00:25:49.736 --> 00:25:52.155
It's my late father's name.

00:25:54.616 --> 00:25:56.826
"Yeong" as in "outstanding,"
and "sik" as in "to plant."

00:25:58.953 --> 00:26:00.246
The perfect name for a tree, right?

00:26:02.749 --> 00:26:06.336
I hope you grow strong like my father.

00:26:08.671 --> 00:26:11.216
