00:32:05.820 --> 00:32:06.946
Here.

00:32:07.030 --> 00:32:08.322
Thank you.

00:32:40.730 --> 00:32:41.939
You know,

00:32:42.732 --> 00:32:44.817
you're just like my dad in some ways.

00:32:46.069 --> 00:32:47.153
What do you mean?

00:32:47.737 --> 00:32:48.821
My dad

00:32:49.989 --> 00:32:52.283
used to be a taxi driver.

00:32:52.366 --> 00:32:54.702
Whenever I found myself in trouble,

00:32:55.286 --> 00:32:57.121
he appeared out of nowhere.

00:32:58.081 --> 00:32:59.332
On rainy days,

00:33:00.374 --> 00:33:02.794
he'd just suddenly pop out of nowhere
with an umbrella.

00:33:03.920 --> 00:33:05.046
If I ever got hurt,

00:33:06.297 --> 00:33:09.258
I'd suddenly find myself on his back
as he ran to get me help.

00:33:09.926 --> 00:33:12.095
It was as if we had telepathy
or something.

00:33:14.639 --> 00:33:16.974
And you're like that too.

00:33:19.352 --> 00:33:21.312
Even now, you're by my side.

00:33:23.523 --> 00:33:25.191
It's really amazing.

00:33:27.568 --> 00:33:28.945
You're being looked out for.

00:33:29.487 --> 00:33:30.321
Sorry?

00:33:34.283 --> 00:33:35.326
As your father,

00:33:36.702 --> 00:33:38.287
he must've been looking out for you.

00:33:39.997 --> 00:33:41.999
And despite the distance,
the worry remains.

00:33:50.967 --> 00:33:51.801
Right.

00:33:52.802 --> 00:33:54.220
I was so lost

00:33:55.054 --> 00:33:56.848
after my dad passed away.

00:33:57.890 --> 00:33:59.725
I didn't let it show in front of my mom…

00:34:01.727 --> 00:34:04.188
but his absence felt so big to me.

00:34:15.825 --> 00:34:17.243
Is that why you married young?

00:34:19.620 --> 00:34:20.621
Because you wanted to

00:34:22.081 --> 00:34:24.083
fill the void your dad left?

00:34:29.213 --> 00:34:30.339
I'm not sure.

00:34:31.632 --> 00:34:34.010
But I guess that's a possibility.

00:34:38.598 --> 00:34:39.807
You could've taken it a little slower.

00:34:41.392 --> 00:34:42.643
What was the rush?

00:34:43.978 --> 00:34:44.854
Pardon?

00:34:47.231 --> 00:34:48.274
It's nothing.

00:34:51.903 --> 00:34:53.654
I wonder when this rain will stop.

00:34:57.742 --> 00:34:58.993
When can we get back up there?

00:34:59.076 --> 00:35:00.953
We'll see if we can in an hour.

00:35:01.037 --> 00:35:03.247
-What happened?
-Hey, Mr. Kim.

00:35:03.331 --> 00:35:04.916
Luckily, Mr. Gong found her.

00:35:04.999 --> 00:35:06.626
