00:38:40.047 --> 00:38:41.382
When people break promises.

00:38:41.465 --> 00:38:42.716
Promises?

00:38:42.800 --> 00:38:45.219
If I promise to brush my teeth
after eating snacks and I don't,

00:38:45.302 --> 00:38:47.763
or if I promise to clean up my toys
and I don't,

00:38:47.847 --> 00:38:48.848
